{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01LVSFVeB6g9LkR8sjnBBMVV","type":"tool_result","content":"=============================================================\nINGRESS-NGINX SECURITY AUDIT FINDINGS\nCluster: karma-local-3  |  Date: 2026-06-25  |  Auditor: automated read-only scan\nController version: ingress-nginx v1.14.1 (nginx/1.27.1)\n=============================================================\n\n--- CRITICAL ---\n\n[C1] CLUSTER-WIDE SECRETS LIST/WATCH IN CLUSTERROLE\n  Resource: ClusterRole/ingress-nginx\n  The ingress-nginx ClusterRole grants list+watch on secrets across ALL\n  namespaces. A compromised controller process can enumerate every TLS\n  secret, service-account token, and opaque secret in the cluster.\n  Remediation: Restrict secret access to the ingress-nginx namespace\n  via a Role, or scope to only secrets with specific label selectors.\n\n--- HIGH ---\n\n[H1] WRITABLE ROOT FILESYSTEM\n  Resource: Deployment/ingress-nginx-controller, container=controller","is_error":false}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"73ea54e6-9d7e-4bde-95ae-683a42f206f2","uuid":"ecb6985a-955d-49c6-be94-7b3045bb854d","timestamp":"2026-06-25T12:55:03.861Z","tool_use_result":{"stdout":"=============================================================\nINGRESS-NGINX SECURITY AUDIT FINDINGS\nCluster: karma-local-3  |  Date: 2026-06-25  |  Auditor: automated read-only scan\nController version: ingress-nginx v1.14.1 (nginx/1.27.1)\n=============================================================\n\n--- CRITICAL ---\n\n[C1] CLUSTER-WIDE SECRETS LIST/WATCH IN CLUSTERROLE\n  Resource: ClusterRole/ingress-nginx\n  The ingress-nginx ClusterRole grants list+watch on secrets across ALL\n  namespaces. A compromised controller process can enumerate every TLS\n  secret, service-account token, and opaque secret in the cluster.\n  Remediation: Restrict secret access to the ingress-nginx namespace\n  via a Role, or scope to only secrets with specific label selectors.\n\n--- HIGH ---\n\n[H1] WRITABLE ROOT FILESYSTEM\n  Resource: Deployment/ingress-nginx-controller, container=controller","stderr":"","interrupted":false,"isImage":false,"noOutputExpected":false}}
{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-sonnet-4-6","id":"msg_016uJiELx9ZdXmxKGZXLanqJ","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"The ConfigMap is created and verified. Here's a summary of the 15 findings across 4 severity tiers:\n\n**Critical (1)**\n- **C1** — ClusterRole grants `list`+`watch` on `secrets` cluster-wide, exposing every TLS cert and service-account token to a compromised controller.\n\n**High (4)**\n- **H1** — `readOnlyRootFilesystem: false` — writable container FS enables attacker persistence.\n- **H2** — `hostPort: 80/443` binds directly to the node NIC, bypassing NetworkPolicy.\n- **H3** — No NetworkPolicy in either `ingress-nginx` or `demo` namespace.\n- **H4** — Conflicting `--watch-ingress-without-class=true` and `=false` flags in the live pod spec; indicates an out-of-band patch not reconciled to source.\n\n**Medium (6)**\n- **M1** — No CPU/memory limits on the controller (only requests).\n- **M2** — `terminationGracePeriodSeconds: 0` drops in-flight connections on restart.\n- **M3** — Two orphaned IngressClass resources (`ingress-1`, `ingress-2`) referencing non-existent controllers.\n- **M4** — ConfigMap `data: null` — no explicit values for `server-tokens`, `ssl-protocols`, HSTS, `proxy-body-size`, or `hide-headers`.\n- **M5** — Tolerations allow scheduling onto master/control-plane nodes.\n- **M6** — `--publish-status-address=localhost` makes Ingress status useless for real routing.\n\n**Low (4)**\n- **L1** — No default IngressClass annotation on any of the three classes.\n- **L2** — No Ingress or Service for the demo app — it is unreachable through nginx.\n- **L3** — `demo-app` Deployment has no resource requests or limits.\n- **L4** — `automountServiceAccountToken: true` explicitly set on the controller SA (noted, not changed).\n\nNo changes were made to any live resource; only the `config-audit` ConfigMap was created in the `demo` namespace."}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"stop_details":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":354,"cache_read_input_tokens":44864,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":354},"output_tokens":1,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"diagnostics":null,"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"73ea54e6-9d7e-4bde-95ae-683a42f206f2","uuid":"ea0b3a1d-f793-46e0-8b0c-46371bad6b2c","request_id":"req_011CcQ1iQLtPEog21iuSeMi2"}
